{"tid":2269292,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣 唔會係陌生嘅厠所屙屎","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T14:00:43.000Z","uid":217062,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"734e1c420a34431dc14cf6b134f7fa6fce2c4a0a","tid":2269292,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"我比屋企人同朋友稱我為黃金屁股<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出街唔會係公廁或者商場屙屎<br />\n<br />\n除非食錯野肚痛要逼住係唔熟悉嘅廁所屙屎之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係都會忍住返到屋企先屙<br />\n<br />\n之前同朋友去旅行，佢哋都會係啲公厠屙屎，我就會返酒店先識急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家都係咪咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26113870e5fc9ed45c653573e31941470896b40a","tid":2269292,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"只會去最高級商場屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neg landmark pp"},{"pid":"d67229d2862eaabcb9d7407f81d753aa1f2f818c","tid":2269292,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26113870e5fc9ed45c653573e31941470896b40a","tid":2269292,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"只會去最高級商場屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neg landmark pp"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"就算高級商場，唔知點解我都係會屙唔到"},{"pid":"321bd78ef9dcf5ed8e63d80f36674beeb31f01f9","tid":2269292,"uid":180999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:40:45.000Z","msg":"搞肚痛點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525ebbc0cc9600b599c53b94df4ad4a48e57d934","tid":2269292,"uid":217062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26113870e5fc9ed45c653573e31941470896b40a","tid":2269292,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,