il.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609043898ea3c5749e6a36a0682ad7b931a8676f","tid":2269292,"uid":217062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9c2b223c4eede695edfa7e0531a0bb4113f62d7","tid":2269292,"uid":139173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"有時出街食錯野肚痛<br />\n真係頂唔順唯有喺街搵廁所去<br />\n去完好有罪惡感<br />\n覺得自己係一個唔潔淨嘅人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過如果真係要係公廁屙<br />\n可唔可以凌空坐馬咁屙呢？<br />\n又或者如果廁所有痞塔，會選擇痞定坐呢？"},{"pid":"a1290499b8b29b2f2fcdce78367289f58f9dd15c","tid":2269292,"uid":205732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"我都係，連肚痛到仆街去商場廁所都痾唔出。<br />\n雖然平時痾尿都係坐喺廁板上面痾，唔會坐無影凳，但係唔知點解真係突破唔到喺街痾屎嘅心理關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f782d907f1e6b9922ba019b7e63c875ead2492","tid":2269292,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T12:26:17.000Z","msg":"鴨片"}]}